comment: Turner's (BOS) contact does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) shot.
RATR shows Williams (TOR) makes contact with Thomas' (BOS) arm on the jump shot.
Olynyk (BOS) makes contact with DeRozan's (TOR) arm and the contact affects his shot.
Turner's (BOS) contact does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) shot.
Olynyk (BOS) cleanly strips the ball from Patterson (TOR).
The contact by Bass (BOS) reroutes Hansbrough (TOR).
Olynyk (BOS) grabs Patterson's (TOR) jersey during the rebounding action and it prevents him from attempting to retrieve the rebound.
Hansbrough (TOR) makes contact with Olynyk's (BOS) wrist and the contact affects his shot.
Bradley (BOS) does not make contact with Williams (TOR).
Williams' (TOR) incidental contact does not affect Turner's (BOS) shot.
Turner (BOS) bumps Patterson (TOR) and knocks him to the floor.
Bass (BOS) dislodges Hansbrough (TOR) and prevents him from retrieving the rebound.
Hansbrough (TOR) makes contact with his right arm when Thomas (BOS) elevates on his drive to the basket.
Zeller (BOS) makes contact with DeRozan's (TOR) arm on the jump shot.
Hansbrough (TOR) grabs Zeller's (BOS) arm.
Crowder (BOS) does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) shot.
Patterson (TOR) commits a take foul on Bass (BOS).
Valanciunas (TOR) makes contact with Smart (BOS) that does not prevent him from attempting to retrieve the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Williams (TOR) was behind the three-point line on his successful field goal was upheld.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Smart (BOS) released the ball on his successful field goal before time expired was upheld.
